snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
PowerWash Simulator is now available on Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, Windows and Steam! It is also live on Xbox and PC Gamepass!

More info on super satisfying virtual pressure washing is here: https://powerwash-simulator.square-enix-games.com/en-gb/

Play PowerWash Simulator on Steam here: https://steamcommunity.com/app/1290000

For more pressure washing goodness subscribe to our channel!
Follow our Twitter for daily satisfying content: https://bit.ly/TwitterPWS
Join our Discord to join the conversation: https://discord.gg/powerwashsimulator
Follow us on TikTok for quick spray socials: https://bit.ly/PWSTikTok

#PowerWashSimulator #Powerwashing #Pressurewashing #Gaming #Games #IndieGame #IndieDev

We are FuturLab and can't wait for you to play the latest update for our power washing game!
